                    <span>This is a well written book and very timely as action is being taken to renovate the Lincoln Cottage.  I reside on the grounds of the Soldiers' Home where the cottage is located and know the value of the cottage in our history. The facility is now known as the Armed Forces Retirement Home-Washington. The cottage has always been known as the Anderson Cottage.</span>
                  
              
